title: India to become one of top five markets for Maybach brand: Mercedes
description: Mercedes-Benz India has launched the electric version of its first-ever all-electric Mercedes-Maybach, the EQS 680 SUV, starting at Rs 2.25 crore. The company aims to make India one of the top five markets for its Maybach brand, highlighting the growth potential and focus on luxury electric mobility.
